smw-pa-property-predefined__sbl_parentpa: !!FUZZY!!"$1" is a predefined property that can describe a relationship between a parent and a child page to help outline a descendant hierarchy for annotated pages and is provided by the [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Breadcrumb_Links Semantic Breadcrumb Links] extension.
